This shall be a benchmark for future anthologies. @NetflixIndia @netflix

text:
BSM (Before SocialMedia) 

You felt happy😄seeing people happy🤗 
You felt sad😢seeing people Sad😞😔 

ASM (After SocialMedia)

You feel sad😔 to see people happy😊 
And very happy😄 to see people sad😒👏🏼

As we watch negativity engulf us & feel helpless 

#WorldPoetryDay 😇
